Package: WaterStrideR
Title: Leg Measurement, Sex and Wing Prediction for Microvelia longipes
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Arthur", "Gairin-Calvo", , "arthur.gairin-calvo@ens-lyon.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Image analysis, statistical, logical tools and pipeline for
    leg measurement, sex and wing prediction of Microvelia longipes
    (Hemiptera, Gerroidea, Veliidae) from images including multiple
    individuals. Scaling is automatized if the image include a millimetric
    orange-red ruler.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/arthurgc-sci/WaterStrideR
